Text: So how do i run this, and install it?
Dan if you have win7 drop the files into a folder call garmin/maps. On mine it is c:/ProgramData/GARMIN/Maps
If you have win7 on your pc put the files in C:/ProgramData/GARMIN/Maps Make sure you have mapsource version 6137 installed first.
you do not need a map id just build your map with mapsource and send it to your unit or sd card
